msgctxt "an7.92:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.92:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. An Ascetic"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 92. Arahāsutta → arahattadhammasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.92:0.3"
msgid "92. Arahāsutta"
msgstr "92. A Perfected One"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.92:1.1"
msgid "“Ārakattā arahā hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, it’s by being far from seven things that you become a perfected "
"one."

msgctxt "an7.92:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.92:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sakkāyadiṭṭhi ārakā hoti, vicikicchā ārakā hoti, sīlabbataparāmāso ārako "
"hoti, rāgo ārako hoti, doso ārako hoti, moho ārako hoti, māno ārako hoti."
msgstr ""
"Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, greed, "
"hate, delusion, and conceit."

msgctxt "an7.92:1.4"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sattannaṃ dhammānaṃ ārakattā arahā hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of being far from these seven things that you become a "
"perfected one.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.92:1.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
